{"tid":779165,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC/MAC/PS4/XBOX] 招人玩War Thunder戰爭雷霆","createTime":"2018-08-14T08:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T11:54:20.000Z","uid":164307,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a0f5770354a453d4ae21d509dd1faeab6e6b56","tid":779165,"uid":164307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:25:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">War Thunder戰爭雷霆</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/151904_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F151904_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=a5977ab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWar Thunder响2016年正式面世，由Gaigin Entertainment(蝸牛公司)發行，主打寫實歴史載具戰爭。呢隻game免費之餘，你仲可以飛天循地，由戰機玩到去戰車，任君選擇。未來更加會推出戰艦，但暫時仍然係封測緊，你當然可以課金買package搶先體驗，但我就寧願等啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/152741_8e2bdea70b925fa4fbf25d1542ce8eb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F152741_8e2bdea70b925fa4fbf25d1542ce8eb1.jpg&h=276ecbed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGame入面你有多個國家近千種載具可以體驗，包括英美法意德日俄，由二戰載具玩到冷戰時期。有傳聞指蝸牛繼戰艦之後將會推出冷戰戰機同攻擊直升機，但是否屬實仍有待觀察。<br />\n<br />\nWar Thunder主要分幾種模式:<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Ground Force/Aviation Arcade Mode</strong>: 簡單戰鬥模式，戰鬥之中會以載具既BR(Battle Rating)作為分房，不論所屬載具國家都會被編成一隊，以16vs16形式作戰。<br />\n地面戰車戰鬥玩家只有三次重生機會，被偵察既敵方載具會响小地圖標示，瞄準系統亦有輔助marker方便射擊。<br />\n而係空戰之中，戰機可以多次重生，而敵方戰機同樣會顯示响雷達，瞄準會有一條預測轉向線方便瞄準。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Realistic Battles</strong>: 寫實戰鬥模式，載具既BR同簡單模式有出入，而且僅會將同陣營既玩家放埋一齊。<br />\n空戰之中，玩家只有一次機會，敵方戰機只有進入偵察範圍先會顯示，戰機彈藥係有限制，而且瞄準係冇瞄準線。<br />\n地面戰係寫實模式有別於空中戰，玩家除咗可以帶戰車之外亦可以帶戰機，遊戲會以擊殺數作為重生籌碼，而敵方載具係並唔會顯示出黎，瞄準亦冇任何輔助。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Simulator Battles</strong>: 模擬戰役模式，佢係咁多個模式之中最難玩既，只有空戰模式。因為遊戲係模擬真實情況，玩家只有第一人稱視角，而且必需由機場起飛去戰埸，總之就好L麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既join我哋discord啦。<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/hgZgPcW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FhgZgPcW&d=7%2FGlMB%2F%2B1qOC0kvt7OfS3BxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=0bf07b0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/hgZgPcW</a>"},{"pid":"491af550601bf61d1f8a56ec644e6817d9d8f3bc","tid":779165,"uid":164307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  PUSH"},{"pid":"f8d0ef8a63f92fdbf0441cc5f461374a01646ab7","tid":779165,"uid":164307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T12:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> PUSH"},{"pid":"56a8eba3d3963818f91b71c0a63372685acbde85","tid":779165,"uid":164307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T20:35:34.000Z","msg":"伴你揸火箭，載你到天空去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9901d7418e92e89e91b109658f88639eff80bd","tid":779165,"uid":6224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T09:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced4a3808c4ccdbbcb67312b33220de9eccbae0b","tid":779165,"uid":38891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:31:42.000Z","msg":"直升機出先定海戰出先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0b8ea25a9ffe5895814753c6303bb0a835e6aa","tid":779165,"uid":164307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ced4a3808c4ccdbbcb67312b33220de9eccbae0b","tid":779165,"uid":38891,"like":0,"dislike":0